{"tid":655083,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖一星期, 男友就想做親蜜行為...","createTime":"2018-05-06T08:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T18:31:03.000Z","uid":129221,"like":43,"dislike":352,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2606a173cb3b7310aa9058220695526e357f84","tid":655083,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"識左男朋友三四個月,上星期佢同我表白 ,我對佢都有好感,就一齊左,但一星期唔夠, 男朋友就想錫我, 我仲未接受到咁快就做呢d親蜜行為 , 加上聞到佢有陣口臭, 就推開左佢, 點知佢就好愕然咁, 仲話佢以前拍拖第一日就會咁做, 唔明點解我接受唔到...<br />\n<br />\n我聽完更加唔開心, 點解要搵我同第2 d女仔比較 , 跟住我就反擊佢話我之前d男朋友都唔會咁口臭啦, 佢就勁嬲, 我又唔開心 , 最後搞左成日先互相氹返大家, 和好返, 但我心中都有條刺 , 估唔到拍左一星期就已經罵架喇..."},{"pid":"a29311e29e4ee34b59f883ee2ef17668c05b2c03","tid":655083,"uid":36296,"like":136,"dislike":3,"score":133,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"0620aa1b5ab192805cc1c923c340542ae435d97b","tid":655083,"uid":9286,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"有條刺 好快會散 分手啦"},{"pid":"8a6b0aa94e48d1f5158271dec882ab091b61072d","tid":655083,"uid":144325,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:01:57.000Z","msg":"刷牙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0006f40a6f9cf39c89aa71868ea510ec33e6b0a5","tid":655083,"uid":117811,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"口臭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4573ddf93fb996385aa5fb9c897541cbb9337f","tid":655083,"uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb95525e9d88f668ec0a3817c824c91c8d0e43d","tid":655083,"uid":148185,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"